Business Unit: Required field. Needs to match the AP code for associated property exactly
GL Account: Required field. Needs to match the GL Code exactly
Period Month: Required field. Must be a number between 1-12, representing the month of the period for which the budget is specified
Period Year: Required field. Must be a 4-digit year for which the budget is specified
Amount: Required field. Budget amount, to 2 decimal places. Numeric only; omit all denomination characters and commas.
Integration Package: Required field. Must match  integration package name selected during upload.
